sources.title: The Girl Swappers (1962) MOTORCYCLE ROMANCE
sources.description:
♥ 1st TIME on YouTUBE ♥
It's Friday@PizzaFLIX
Director: Freddie Francis
Stars: George Chakiris, Jackie Lane, Janette Scott

A US airman stationed in the UK strikes down his commanding officer. Believing he killed him, the airman goes on the run with his girl. They cross paths with another couple and a mix-up occurs.
